  <brief_title>Pharmacokinetics and Safety of Evogliptin in Subjects With Hepatic Dysfunction</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study to Evaluate Pharmacokinetics and Safety of Evogliptin in Subjects With Hepatic Dysfunction and Control Healthy Volunteers</official_title>
