  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of the study is to compare the pharmacokinetics profiles and safety of
      Evogliptin in patients wit hepatic dysfunction versus healthy volunteers after single oral
      dose of Evogliptin
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      When the future evogliptin be administered to liver dysfunction patients, to investgate
      whether dose adjustment is necessary.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
